( ) Tj
T*
(## 5\\) Rotation Update from Direction) Tj
T*
( ) Tj
T*
(Code pattern:) Tj
T*
( ) Tj
T*
(```csharp) Tj
T*
(float angle = Mathf.Atan2\\(nextDirection.y, nextDirection.x\\) * Mathf.Rad2Deg;) Tj
T*
(transform.rotation = Quaternion.Euler\\(0, 0, angle + projectileRotationOffset\\);) Tj
T*
(```) Tj
T*
( ) Tj
T*
(Math meaning:) Tj
T*
( ) Tj
T*
(- `atan2\\(y, x\\)` gives heading angle of vector `\\(x, y\\)`.) Tj
T*
(- Convert rad -> deg for Unity rotation APIs.) Tj
T*
(- Add sprite offset if your sprite forward axis is not +X.) Tj
T*
( ) Tj
T*
(In this project:) Tj
T*
( ) Tj
T*
(- `ProjectileRotationOffset = -90f` because spear art orientation requires correction.) Tj
T*
( ) Tj
T*
(## 6\\) Why Pooling Needed `OnTriggerStay2D`) Tj
T*
( ) Tj
T*
(When a pooled spear is re-enabled, enemies may already overlap the homing trigger.) Tj
T*
( ) Tj
T*
(- `OnTriggerEnter2D` may not fire immediately for pre-existing overlaps.) Tj
T*
(- `OnTriggerStay2D` guarantees overlapping enemies are tracked on subsequent physics ticks.) Tj
T*
( ) Tj
T*
(So pooling-safe target collection uses both callbacks.) Tj
T*
( ) Tj
T*
(## 7\\) Stability Guards You Should Always Keep) Tj
T*
( ) Tj
T*
(- Skip homing if target list is empty.) Tj
T*
(- Ignore null/inactive enemies.) Tj
T*
(- Ignore near-zero direction vectors before normalize.) Tj
T*
(- Keep list deduplicated.) Tj
T*
( ) Tj
T*
(These prevent jitter, invalid vectors, and stale pooled references.) Tj
T*
( ) Tj
T*
(## 8\\) Practical Tuning Cheat Sheet) Tj
T*
( ) Tj
T*
(- `homingTurnSpeedDegrees = 180` -> very soft turns.) Tj
T*
(- `homingTurnSpeedDegrees = 360` -> moderate turns.) Tj
T*
(- `homingTurnSpeedDegrees = 720` -> aggressive turns.) Tj
T*
(- `homingTurnSpeedDegrees = 1080+` -> almost snap-like.) Tj
T*
( ) Tj
T*
(Start around `540-720` and tune by feel.) Tj
T*
( ) Tj
T*
(## 9\\) Mapping to Current Code) Tj
T*
( ) Tj
T*
(- Target selection: `WeaponSpear.TryGetNearestTarget\\(...\\)`) Tj
T*
(- Steering: `WeaponSpear.SteerTowardsTarget\\(...\\)`) Tj
T*
(- Continuous homing loop: `WeaponSpear.FixedUpdate\\(\\)` -> `UpdateContinuousHoming\\(\\)`) Tj
T*
(- Pool-safe enemy tracking: `WeaponTriggerHoming.OnTriggerEnter2D/OnTriggerStay2D`) Tj
T*
ET
